Responsiveness & UX/UI

Fully responsive: application must be optimized for different screen sizes used today, including:

Small mobile (320px+)

Large mobile

Tablets

Laptops

Desktops

Large displays (4K, etc.)

Use mobile-first CSS approach.

Leverage TailwindCSS breakpoints properly.

