Provide full keyboard navigation and focus management.

Respect color contrast accessibility standards.

Add tabIndex, aria-label, and on:keydown where interactive.

Logical heading hierarchy and alt text for images.

API Integration

Use real backend API calls for all functionality.

Ensure proper error handling and loading states for API requests.

Implement proper authentication and authorization headers.

Use environment variables for API configuration.

